WORN

Syntax: worn

Displays all armor and equipment your character currently has equipped,
organized by wear slot.

WEAR SLOTS (common)
  head          helmet, hat, or headgear
  face          visor, mask, or faceplate
  body          torso armor or jacket
  arms          arm guards or gauntlets
  hands         gloves
  legs          leg armor
  feet          boots or greaves
  back          backpack or cape
  belt          holsters, pouches

NOTES
  Each slot can only hold one item at a time (some exceptions apply).
  Armor protects based on its MDC or AR/SDC rating.
  MDC armor absorbs MDC weapon damage before it reaches your MDC pool.
  When armor MDC reaches 0 it is destroyed.

RELATED COMMANDS
  inventory (inv)    shows items you are carrying
  wear <item>        puts on a piece of armor or clothing
  wield <item>       readies a weapon for combat
  remove <item>      takes off a worn item

See also: inventory, combat, wear, wield
